export const config = {
  "automaticRearrangeAfterDropNode": false,
  "collapsible": false,
  "directed": false,
  "focusAnimationDuration": 0,
  "focusZoom": 1,
  "height": 500,
  "highlightDegree": 1,
  "highlightOpacity": 1,
  "linkHighlightBehavior": false,
  "maxZoom": 8,
  "minZoom": 0.1,
  "nodeHighlightBehavior": true,
  "panAndZoom": false,
  "staticGraph": false,
  "staticGraphWithDragAndDrop": false,
  "width": 1300,
  "d3": {
    "alphaTarget": 0.05,
    "gravity": -50,
    "linkLength": 80,
    "linkStrength": 1,
    "disableLinkForce": false
  },
    "node": {
      "color": "DarkKhaki",
      "fontColor": "black",
      "fontSize": 8,
      "fontWeight": "normal",
      "highlightColor": "#a189a0",
      "highlightFontSize": 8,
      "highlightFontWeight": "normal",
      "highlightStrokeColor": "#a189a0",
      "highlightStrokeWidth": "SAME",
      "labelProperty": "id",
      "mouseCursor": "pointer",
      "opacity": 1,
      "renderLabel": false,
      "size": 200,
      "strokeColor": "none",
      "strokeWidth": 1.5,
      "svg": "",
      "symbolType": "circle"
    },
    "link": {
      "color": "#d3d3d3",
      "fontColor": "black",
      "fontSize": 8,
      "fontWeight": "normal",
      "highlightColor": "#a189a0",
      "highlightFontSize": 8,
      "highlightFontWeight": "normal",
      "labelProperty": "label",
      "mouseCursor": "pointer",
      "opacity": 1,
      "renderLabel": false,
      "semanticStrokeWidth": false,
      "strokeWidth": 1.5,
      "markerHeight": 6,
      "markerWidth": 6
    }
  }

  export default config;
